<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">4</FONT> &nbsp; Belistiche, the concubine of Ptolemaeus, wins the Olympic prize in the race for pairs of foals.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">5</FONT> &nbsp; The Romans capture Vulsinii, and take ruthless action to restore order.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">6</FONT> &nbsp; The Carthaginian garrison is forced to withdraw from Messana.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">8</FONT> &nbsp; The Carthaginians and Syracusans combine to besiege Messana.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">9</FONT> &nbsp; C.Claudius is defeated while attempting to cross over to Sicily.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">11</FONT> &nbsp; Ap.Claudius crosses over to Sicily.
