<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">9</FONT> &nbsp; Hieron of Syracuse changes sides and becomes an ally of the Romans.
<BR><FONT CLASS="ref">14</FONT> &nbsp; Valerius adopts the cognomen of Messalla, in recognition of the help he gave to the inhabitants of Messana.
<P CLASS="sidep"><A HREF="year262.html">262  B.C.</A>
